{"tid":890632,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"腳底根膜炎 有冇人醫好？","createTime":"2018-11-05T12:45:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T14:52:18.000Z","uid":197926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"3e33f65d68079540a7e4401cc730e1bc1c43ac36","tid":890632,"uid":197926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T12:45:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求助！🙏"},{"pid":"24529e819925f5a5b0fb924430e6950260c2cfa6","tid":890632,"uid":52271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T12:47:55.000Z","msg":"以前試過<br />\n得閒銳下佢/搵網球碌下<br />\n都唔得的話試下搵人針炙"},{"pid":"e03e837069aaf45a64ffc2fd943e739f96507951","tid":890632,"uid":76105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T12:54:52.000Z","msg":"試過 。直頭痛到行唔到路，睇跌打敷藥都唔work <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  上網睇 踩高爾夫球或者圓形嘅野。<br />\n<br />\n主要銳落你痛果條筋，慢慢銳番鬆。一開頭超痛，每日十分鐘。好快好番 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a341c554c4400dda9fbe7be786698b59818eb7","tid":890632,"uid":26274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T12:54:54.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"0a5d8846f961371e84663d58f502ccd7a82a9ef5","tid":890632,"uid":76105,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T12:58:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h5x3z1N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh5x3z1N.png&h=fa09b8ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果無，可以試吓圓形一支支嘅野。都有用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fEAkCfN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfEAkCfN.png&h=424e2450&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b70ffdc1e02f53b39a262d0d9785f570867d8a30","tid":890632,"uid":207328,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T14:07:16.000Z","msg":"斬撚咗佢就無事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6abdc0c4e55d9f34172a2252c93dd6c236f2d1b","tid":890632,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T16:16:39.000Z","msg":"朝朝落床 腳板底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1283411d1ab337be4be097452f8153a5a6b33c7d","tid":890632,"uid":197926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T16:17:22.000Z","msg":"我買左個新鞋墊support個足弓，好DD.<br />\n但一禁落去腳根附近都係痛，差唔多兩個月了。 有冇人試過衝擊波治療？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n感謝巴打回答🙏"},{"pid":"26a31cb94b2ad0c9d09501603f8efd5ebfd4c5f3","tid":890632,"uid":197926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6abdc0c4e55d9f34172a2252c93dd6c236f2d1b","tid":890632,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T16:16:39.000Z","msg":"朝朝落床 腳板底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T16:19:04.000Z","msg":"一開頭落床超痛，之後冇野。過左兩星期就行路都有痛。 反反覆覆⋯⋯好想斷尾"},{"pid":"e6cabb345edea6da008586fb4ecea87f8a5f65ec","tid":890632,"uid":212316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T16:23:18.000Z","msg":"我曾經發過炎，跛住行，但自己睇兩三次跌打貼中藥，三個星期好番"},{"pid":"be8c90feaacb06e2685d3bcab37937cda411e19e","tid":890632,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26a31cb94b2ad0c9d09501603f8efd5ebfd4c5f3","tid":890632,"uid":197926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6abdc0c4e55d9f34172a2252c93dd6c236f2d1b","tid":890632,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T16:16:39.000Z","msg":"朝朝落床 腳板底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T16:19:04.000Z","msg":"一開頭落床超痛，之後冇野。過左兩星期就行路都有痛。 反反覆覆⋯⋯好想斷尾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T16:25:09.000Z","msg":"我而家選鞋好小心<br />\n<br />\n拖鞋 揀AEON 或 日本城 某一隻日本拖<br />\n<br />\n出家著 for over