/>\n睇醫生, 消炎藥, 腳浸中藥, 活洛油等<br />\n鞋加軟墊, 著吸震力高的鞋 (腳板筋肌太舒服, 日久失去承托力量)<br />\n以為日日坐同訓係對病情好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T03:35:01.000Z","msg":"唔好著有太多support ge鞋就岩啦<br />\n肌肉唔練就會冇"},{"pid":"2fb9c6a81468a7d1afd4b85005822fc4ab56e444","tid":890632,"uid":197926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41582382564a075c834a763fc66c72e368ad49bb","tid":890632,"uid":12742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T01:14:20.000Z","msg":"減肥先啦，我一減咗就無事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T06:18:14.000Z","msg":"原本幾重？減到幾重呀<br />\n我成220 磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7549fa2d90572b05a242caf3d56a908124e6ae5a","tid":890632,"uid":197926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"739ca65c9b4db858b7c65dc0ce33dc9f780821fd","tid":890632,"uid":20592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T01:29:22.000Z","msg":"份工著d垃圾安全鞋仲要行得太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身一直都係少少痛<br />\n<br />\n半年前去日本著錯鞋睇左5日rock fest又企又跳足十粒鐘日 個fd要痴藥膚住先行到<br />\n<br />\n我就返香港之後到e家都仲痛緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加埋份閪工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 拎圓柱體同按條筋係有用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T06:19:14.000Z","msg":"巴打係腳邊個位痛，有d巴打係足弓痛"},{"pid":"e2e1718273e3c8510ce4febf3ceefc3328f5b9fd","tid":890632,"uid":197926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T12:57:23.000Z","msg":"早兩星期，好番好多，起身落床，冇痛，家下又痛番。好煩呀⋯⋯<br />\n可能果個星期晚晚浸熱水，同用鞋墊，行多左反而好好多。<br />\n最近停左浸熱水又痛番，行都痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b406fe0774d98eef9bf82e54c0cbacdc6336e1a","tid":890632,"uid":197926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:09:18.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打做過衝擊波治療？ work唔work 呀？"},{"pid":"09d2fc21808a8affcb0cad3bbe9a88c5213fd31f","tid":890632,"uid":33065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-1